&lt;p&gt;Hope you like&amp;nbsp;it!&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Pablo Iranzo Gómez</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 12 Oct 2020 20:32:34 +0200</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:iranzo.io,2020-10-12:/blog/2020/10/12/lego-porsche-911-led-kit/</guid><category>blog</category><category>lego</category><category>42056</category><category>Porsche</category><category>911</category><category>LED kit</category><category>GT3 RS</category></item><item><title>Lego Bugatti Chiron and Porsche 911 GT3 RS</title><link>https://iranzo.io/blog/2020/02/21/lego-bugatti-chiron-and-porsche-911-gt3-rs/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Here you can see a photo comparison between &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.es/dp/B01CCT2ZHC?tag=redken-21"&gt;Porsche 911 &lt;span class="caps"&gt;GT3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="caps"&gt;RS&lt;/span&gt; 🛒&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.es/dp/B0792RB3B6?tag=redken-21"&gt;Bugatti Chiron 🛒&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
